# 🔴 THIS FILE USED TO IGNORE package.json AND package-lock.json.
#
# Which meant that anyone who cloned this repository — including you, on a new
# machine — would find no `npm test`, no `npm run e2e`, and no pinned dependency
# versions. The 408 engine tests and 176 UI tests would have been unrunnable, and
# the whole claim that "a failing test cannot ship" would have been decoration.
#
# A test suite you cannot run is not a test suite. Both files are now COMMITTED,
# deliberately, and the lockfile is committed BECAUSE it pins jsdom and Playwright
# to the exact versions the suite was verified against.

node_modules/

# Playwright output
test-results/
playwright-report/
blob-report/

# scratch
*.tmp
*.tmp.js
.e.tmp
.t.tmp
